Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,=================text===============
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.00,0:00:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 会被旁边的人看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.59,0:00:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那我来帮你藏起来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.30,0:00:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,凉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.87,0:00:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,叫我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.62,0:00:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,凉…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.79,0:00:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,凉…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.33,0:01:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,凉 这样很羞耻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.93,0:01:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,凉 我已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.41,0:01:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,静歌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.05,0:01:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.99,0:01:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我在这种地方做着这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.96,0:01:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,凉一直都这么强硬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.44,0:01:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我却没能反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.17,0:01:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我可能对凉…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.98,0:01:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐你怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.26,0:01:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我是因为太无聊了就出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.20,0:01:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,难道说你也是?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.64,0:01:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,凑近一看更是美人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.26,0:01:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那一起逃出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.14,0:02:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫雾岛凉 请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.81,0:02:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫小南静歌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.00,0:02:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,最初只是当作年长漂亮的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.90,0:02:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你是凉?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.94,0:02:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,说回来你还是第一次看到我素颜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.51,0:02:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,变得不知所措
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.89,0:02:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.87,0:02:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,都怪我让你有了害怕的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.44,0:02:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.12,0:02:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.76,0:02:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然外表经常被人说是轻浮的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.80,0:02:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.40,0:02:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不认真的话就不会这么执着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.61,0:02:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,凉 我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.19,0:02:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 要下了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.68,0:02:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,这样就没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.57,0:03:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,从旁边看也没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.22,0:03:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得应该没事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.14,0:03:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,应该…怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.07,0:03:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,感谢乘坐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.62,0:03:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,请小心脚下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.49,0:03:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.59,0:03:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,完全放晴了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.87,0:03:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.06,0:03:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.79,0:03:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来乘什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.83,0:03:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,凉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.67,0:03:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…谢谢你的外套
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.40,0:03:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不要客气
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.65,0:03:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,静歌 怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.90,0:03:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直都在得到凉的帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.33,0:03:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道该怎么回报
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.78,0:03:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不要介意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.34,0:03:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是在做我喜欢的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.46,0:04:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 我还没有回复凉的那份心意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.24,0:04:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,那么下次再这样约会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.91,0:04:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,下次想去咖啡厅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.85,0:04:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,静歌你能和我一起去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.37,0:04:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.16,0:04:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,凉
